&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.strava.com/segments/20320250&quot; class=&quot;external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;Bogenberg- Lippweg&lt;/a&gt;: 0,74 km, 14,6% Steigung, 109 HM&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.strava.com/segments/29827140&quot; class=&quot;external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;Quellweg uphill&lt;/a&gt;: 0,38 km, 8,0% Steigung, 33 HM&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.strava.com/segments/29829856&quot; class=&quot;external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;Hangweg uphill&lt;/a&gt;: 0,55 km, 18,8% Steigung, 105 HM &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
